code: @Override @After public void tearDown() throws Exception {     super.tearDown().     // test may be skipped so we did not create a parser instance     if (parser != null) {         // next token can be null even in the middle of the document (e.g. with "---"), but not too many consecutive times         assertThat(parser.currentToken(), nullValue()).         assertThat(parser.nextToken(), nullValue()).         assertThat(parser.nextToken(), nullValue()).         parser.close().     } }
